description: Multiplicative order of 10 mod n, where gcd(n, 10) = 1.
mathematica: MultiplicativeOrder[10, #] & /@ Select[ Range@ 190, GCD[10, #] == 1 &] (* _Robert G. Wilson v_, Apr 05 2011 *)
prog: (PARI) lista(nn) = {for (n=1, nn, if (gcd(n,10) == 1, print1(znorder(Mod(10, n)), ", ")););} \\ _Michel Marcus_, Feb 06 2015
author: _David W. Wilson_
